{"word":"ὁμοίως","slug":"ὁμοίως","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὁμοίως</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὅμοιος\">ὅμοιος</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>likewise, in similar manner, similarly <a href='B:470 22:26'>Mt 22:26</a>; <a href='B:470 26:35'>26:35</a>; <a href='B:480 15:31'>Mk 15:31</a>; <a href='B:490 3:11'>Lk 3:11</a>; <a href='B:490 6:31'>6:31</a>; <a href='B:490 10:37'>10:37</a>; <a href='B:490 16:25'>16:25</a></b> (the focus is on the experience of receipt as such); <b><a href='B:500 5:19'>J 5:19</a>; <a href='B:500 6:11'>6:11</a>; <a href='B:500 21:13'>21:13</a>; <a href='B:520 1:27'>Ro 1:27</a>; <a href='B:530 7:22'>1 Cor 7:22</a>; <a href='B:650 9:21'>Hb 9:21</a>; <a href='B:660 2:25'>Js 2:25</a>; <a href='B:670 3:1'>1 Pt 3:1</a>, <a href='B:670 3:7'>7</a></b> (here <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> focus on reciprocity responding to wifely action); <b><a href='B:720 1:1'>Jd 8</a>; <a href='B:730 2:15'>Rv 2:15</a>; <a href='B:730 8:12'>8:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὁμοίωμα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὁμοίωσις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}